---
title: A Minimal Painter's Gallery
description: Quiet rooms of color, light, and form.
layout: base
---

<h2 style="margin-left: 10px">Gallery</h2>
<ul
    class="gallery-grid"
    webc:if="collections.paintings && collections.paintings.length > 0"
>
    <li class="gallery-card" webc:for="painting of collections.paintings">
        <a class="gallery-link" :href="url(painting.url)">
            <div>
                <img
                    :src="url(`/images/${painting.fileSlug}.jpg`)"
                    :alt="painting.data.title"
                    loading="lazy"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-meta">
                <h3 class="gallery-title" @text="painting.data.title"></h3>
                <p class="gallery-details">
                    <span @text="painting.data.medium"></span> â€”
                    <span @text="painting.data.year"></span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </li>
</ul>

<p webc:if="!collections.paintings || collections.paintings.length === 0">
    No paintings yet. Add markdown files in the
    <code>paintings</code> collection.
</p>
